1. create normal ec2 instance and login.
2. sudo -i
3. vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config
4. line no-63 (PasswordAuthentication yes)
5. service sshd restart
6. sudo passwd root [give own password] `incase if you want to give own user, give own name as root place. Ex:sudo passwd masthan
7. ssh root@public-ip of ec2
8. give password and login.
